Aalap Studio Presents:- New Nepali Tele Serial MAYAKO CHINO EPISODE-12 Only on Aalap Studio Official Youtube Channel  

"MAYAKO CHINO" is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

localized.description:
Aalap Studio Presents:- New Nepali Tele Serial MAYAKO CHINO EPISODE-12 Only on Aalap Studio Official Youtube Channel  

"MAYAKO CHINO" is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

en.description:
Aalap Studio Presents:- New Nepali Tele Serial MAYAKO CHINO EPISODE-12 Only on Aalap Studio Official Youtube Channel  

"MAYAKO CHINO" is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

snippet.description:
#WhereIsPushpa #Pushpa2TheRule #AlluArjun

Where is Pushpa? Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Hindi Glimpse !!!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Suneel, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing were performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Karthika Srinivas respectively.

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Part 1 ft. Benafsha Soonawalla | Music Prod By @BluishMusic & Sez On The beat
snippet.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity an individual goes through in a relationship, especially women. It's the hard truth that people don't even talk or discuss about in real life. From this song, Dino James has a strong message to the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't linger around and dwell in such relationships and If you are experiencing such behaviour just walk away because you deserve a lot better.

#DinoJames #BoyfriendPart1
